<br>
Water Elemental Form is 4 mana per tick for 36 minutes out of 72 (the water breathing and sta regen is useless at this level.) It costs 18 points<br>
<br>
Air elemental form Gives  25 to all resists and Levitate and see invis. Levitate means it can't be used in zones where lev is off, in other places its basicly just more lag from the bobbing. It is 36 minutes out of 72. Costs 18 points.<br>
<br>
So for 36 points, we can have 2/3 the mana regen of a wizard half the time, and + the same resists half the time. <br>
<br>
<br>
