<br>
I also never said we were the only class not seeing improvement. I said we have been waiting, watching others get improvements, but nothing for us. The one improvement they gave us, they took away again. Until permenant foci are in the game, I am not going to count beta testing focus items as an improvement to our class. If they stack with the dropped/quested foci, then I'll sing my praise to VI, till I see that, I don't consider them much of a boon.<br>
